{"tid":1159914,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【女神崩壞】湯洛雯驚現三截米芝蓮肥肉","createTime":"2019-05-18T05:31:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-18T11:29:53.000Z","uid":137088,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"85c980e9bf69168e9f3a31fcb61f8da209a9baa9","tid":1159914,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T05:31:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190516/photo/bkn-20190516000054196-0516_00862_001_01p.jpg?20190516002055\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190516%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190516000054196-0516_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20190516002055&h=bc0f775e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n湯洛雯要減磅頂替黃心穎（圓圖）拍劇，但就好似中咗「不瘦降」咁，愈減愈肥...<br />\n<br />\n藝人黃心穎爆出偷食人夫許志安後敗走洛杉磯，留下一堆「蘇州屎」要人執手尾，拖累有份參演的劇集《法證先鋒IV》要重拍後才可播映，月初已落實由無綫小花湯洛雯（靚湯）頂替其角色，更被勒令在下月開工前減10磅，當時靚湯對於在開工前搣甩肥肉信心滿滿，但似乎並非想像中簡單！ <br />\n<br />\n不介意「執二攤」的靚湯雖然表示會努力做運動及控制飲食減磅，但隨着開工日子愈來愈近，未知是否壓力太大，其體形似乎不瘦反脹！日前下午，靚湯穿白色吊帶背心及白色短褲打底，外搭一件紅色半透視外套及紗裙，正面看其造型逼爆，巨咪及一雙粗髀若隱若現，背面看起來則虎背熊腰，更驚現三截「米芝蓮肥肉」，吸睛度大減，看來未來兩周要絕食才能達標！ <br />\n<br />\n另一日，靚湯獨自驅車往西九一個商場購物，當日她醒目穿連帽外套襯長褲包到冚，遮掩一團團肥肉。她先去名店閒逛，之後再去附近時裝店睇衫，不一會已揀選了大堆心水往付款。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190516/photo/bkn-20190516000054196-0516_00862_001_02p.jpg?20190516002055\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190516%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190516000054196-0516_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20190516002055&h=e411de76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190516/photo/bkn-20190516000054196-0516_00862_001_03p.jpg?20190516002055\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190516%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190516000054196-0516_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20190516002055&h=6534bb51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190516/photo/bkn-20190516000054196-0516_00862_001_04p.jpg?20190516002055\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190516%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190516000054196-0516_00862_001_04p.jpg%3F20190516002055&h=542c8c26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190516/photo/bkn-20190516000054196-0516_00862_001_05p.jpg?20190516002055\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190516%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190516000054196-0516_00862_001_05p.jpg%3F20190516002055&h=d509e901&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190516/photo/bkn-20190516000054196-0516_00862_001_06p.jpg?20190516002055\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190516%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190516000054196-0516_00862_001_06p.jpg%3F20190516002055&h=8d174029&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190516/photo/bkn-20190516000054196-0516_00862_001_07p.jpg?20190516002055\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190516%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190516000054196-0516_00862_001_07p.jpg%3F20190516002055&h=0c32250e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190516/photo/bkn-20190516000054196-0516_00862_001_08p.jpg?20190516002055\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190516%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190516000054196-0516_00862_001_08p.jpg%3F20190516002055&h=ef272ec7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190516/mobile/bkn-20190516000054196-0516_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190516%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190516000054196-0516_00862_001.html&d=LRk9npnliL4HefRMP%2BWOkGHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=ca0ed2fa\" data-a